              shalbum - http://sourceforge.net/projects/shalbum
              =================================================
                          INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
                       document updated: 20-March-2006


Just issue 'make install', simple as that!

shalbum will be installed to default PREFIX '/usr/local'. You can
override this by adding 'PREFIX=/the/path/you/want' to the make
command-line.

To uninstall run 'make uninstall', pointing the correct PREFIX if
appropriate.

----------------------------------------------------------------------

Installed Files


$(PREFIX)/bin
  shalbum             The script itself.


$(PREFIX)/share/shalbum
  README              General shalbum instructions
  _options            Sample configuration file
  watermark_th.png    Sample watermark for thumbnail
  watermark_vga.png   Sample watermark for final image
